title: LIP-0: Burn the keys to the Loot Contract
body:
Please see the details of the proposal on the community run Loot Talk forum: https://loot-talk.com/t/lip-0-burn-the-keys-to-the-loot-contract/1218

Apologies, but this vote will be duplicative of the existing “Burn the Keys” proposal in order to get a completely fresh start.
